  <Subject Subject_ID="300054071">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300054070</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>injection molding [300054070], molding (forming) [300053134], forming (physical activity) [300053098], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plastics process in which the fast-reacting liquid ingredients of a thermosetting plastic are separately injected into a closed mold in such a way as to achieve intimate mixing. The ensuing reaction causes the mixture to harden rapidly.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000011611/Dietz, Plastics Terminology (1986)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proceso de plásticos en el cual los ingredientes líquidos de reacción rápida de un plástico termofraguable son inyectados por separados en un molde cerrado de modo que alcance una mezcla acabada. La reacción siguiente provoca que la mezcla se endurezca rápidamente.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vormingsproces voor plastic waarbij de snel reagerende, vloeibare ingrediënten van een thermohardende plastic afzonderlijk in een gesloten gietvorm worden gespoten, en wel zodanig dat er een zeer goed mengsel ontstaat. De reactie die volgt, zorgt ervoor dat het mengsel snel hard wordt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052374/Polytechnisch woordenboek En-Ne (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>熱固性塑膠製程中，將數種反應速度快的液態原料分別注入同一閉合模具中，藉由此法可將原料充分混合，而混合物會在後續反應中急速固化。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
